cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.DS 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image segmentation and path classification algorithms. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes an active learning approach to speed up the annotation process. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with developing an algorithm to improve the effectiveness of path classification. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with reducing the training set size without compromising the reconstruction quality. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also a less likely category, but possible as the paper operates on a graph and proposes a new approach to reduce the training set size.
